{"tid":1007484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解藍色會象徵男性，粉紅色象徵女性？","createTime":"2019-02-03T19:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T06:14:47.000Z","uid":199515,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"42c7e9d33643e1d926a3bfe9a273df59e8b73f52","tid":1007484,"uid":199515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"男性果方面冇咁明顯，但市面上for女性既產品都係以粉紅/紅色為主，而女仔用既野、著既衫都會有頗多係粉紅色，反而男人用粉紅色既野同著粉紅色既衫會被人覺得奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （細細個用粉紅色既筆袋被同學笑，阿媽買比細妹既野通常都係粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n究竟係幾時有依種顔色既性別象徵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d5cc956182040d298c8573e540a7983d846df7","tid":1007484,"uid":80176,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:29:51.000Z","msg":"M血=紅=臭闣=女人"},{"pid":"1644f28d36d4ae40ff8cea9751f998418854e44b","tid":1007484,"uid":19214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:33:53.000Z","msg":"我好鐘意粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf093c9b46c337f1fe92cd0926c846300e0d40c1","tid":1007484,"uid":165936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:36:00.000Z","msg":"當年有個比利時極端女權反性別定型左膠話我知係希特拉定嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知堅定流"},{"pid":"90242f1634d5e4c4254cfa52047341489f63ac58","tid":1007484,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:49:56.000Z","msg":"Jacqueline Kennedy當年成日著粉紅套裝露面<br />\n慢慢粉紅就被套上女性化既刻板印象<br />\n之後啲marketing撚又順勢上<br />\n結果變成宜家咁既狀態<br />\n原本一百年前其實係掉返轉"},{"pid":"591ad4930435cd4d3db5f6c37cfd1d9bd4dfe80d","tid":1007484,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:50:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22466b8effc3f7b13c6c8339254926cac2b37c45","tid":1007484,"uid":19214,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"591ad4930435cd4d3db5f6